			<description><![CDATA[<p>
	SoundCloud is looking for an ActionScript/Flash/Flex developer to work&nbsp;on the best audio player on the Internets.</p>
<p>
	Have you ever wanted to build something meaningful&nbsp;&mdash;&nbsp;something that&nbsp;millions of people around the world would be using every day? Or&nbsp;get a personal &lsquo;thank you&rdquo; from your all-time favorite band for&nbsp;your great work? Well, we can make these dreams come true.<br />
	&nbsp;<br />
	You love to learn new things, solve challenges and share your&nbsp;knowledge with the rest of the world. You are already here or you want&nbsp;to move to the currently most-fascinating city in Europe. Oh, and you&nbsp;are absolutely addicted to music and sounds!</p>
<p>
	<strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>
<ul>
	<li>
		Build super-performant and fast-loading audio players and&nbsp;other Flash-based components</li>
	<li>
		Make SoundCloud players work in all browsers, all&nbsp;platforms and all sites</li>
	<li>
		Work closely with and incorporate feedback from&nbsp;product management, interaction designers, and back-end engineers</li>
	<li>
		Rapidly fix bugs and solve problems</li>
	<li>
		Pro-actively look for ways to make SoundCloud better</li>
</ul>
<p>
	&nbsp;<br />
	<strong>Requirements:</strong></p>
<ul>
	<li>
		Great Flash development skills (CPU / memory&nbsp;optimization, External Interface, Cross-browser and FP version&nbsp;compatibility, Flex, AIR)</li>
	<li>
		Top level knowledge of ActionScript3, MXML, MXMLC, Flex&nbsp;Builder/FDT, Git</li>
	<li>
		Great HTML/CSS/Javascript skills</li>
	<li>
		Experience implementing MVC and other design patterns</li>
	<li>
		Experience in the development of Flash Applications&nbsp;with a heavy server communication (Remoting, Sockets, Streaming, JSON)</li>
	<li>
		Disciplined approach to testing and quality assurance,&nbsp;experience in TDD</li>
	<li>
		Good understanding of web technologies and familiarity with Unix</li>
	<li>
		Foundation in design with an eye for pixel-perfect layouts</li>
	<li>
		Great written communication and documentation abilities</li>
</ul>
<p>
	See you in Berlin!</p>
